title: DAZ3D - The Slim Man for G3M
description:
THE SLIM MAN for G3M
--------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/23a0a12e7a2b0c255f4b807be89c2b74.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/33737

This faceless fearsome figure returns to haunt your nightmares. Vaguely human in appearance, but his featureless face and back tentacles reveal the supernatural horror he truly is. Guard your children, stay out of the woods, he is always watching and waiting. The set comes complete with custom crafted High Definition Morphs, and a highly detailed texture set, suitable for Iray and 3Delight
